 contamination.", "Organic farming promotes biodiversity, builds healthy soil, and reduces greenhouse gas emissions.", "Organic agriculture mitigates exposure to harmful chemicals, heavy metals, and antibiotic-resistant bacteria found in conventional practices."]}
