            Level-3 Your Rebuttal: {"claim": "Organic food's higher cost is due to lower yields, not superior efficiency.", "argument": ["Organic farming has lower yields per hectare.", "If organic farming were more efficient, it would be cheaper."]}
            Level-3 Your Rebuttal: {"claim": "The organic movement's rejection of GMOs is a mistake.", "argument": ["The National Research Council sees no fundamental difference between traditional and modern plant modification techniques.", "Genetic modification is faster and more effective than traditional methods."]}
